def Minutesplot(playerlist=Players):
    Col = {"AndrewWiggins":"Black", "BojanBogdanovic":"Red","HarrisonBarnes":"Green","KevinDurant":"Blue","KhrisMiddleton":"Magenta","LeBronJames":"Black", "OttoPorterJr":"Red","PaulGeorge":"Green","TimHardawayJr":"Blue","TJWarren":"Magenta"}
    Mrk = {"AndrewWiggins":"s","BojanBogdanovic":"o","HarrisonBarnes":"^","KevinDurant":"D","KhrisMiddleton":"s","LeBronJames":"o", "OttoPorterJr":"^","PaulGeorge":"D","TimHardawayJr":"s","TJWarren":"o"} 
    for name in playerlist:        
        plt.plot(MinutesPlayed[PlayerD[name]], c=Col[name], ls='--', marker=Mrk[name], ms=7, label=name)
    plt.legend(loc='upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1))
    plt.xticks(list(range(0,7)), Month)
    plt.show()

def FieldGoalsplot(playerlist=Players):
    Col = {"AndrewWiggins":"Black", "BojanBogdanovic":"Red","HarrisonBarnes":"Green","KevinDurant":"Blue","KhrisMiddleton":"Magenta","LeBronJames":"Black", "OttoPorterJr":"Red","PaulGeorge":"Green","TimHardawayJr":"Blue","TJWarren":"Magenta"}
    Mrk = {"AndrewWiggins":"s","BojanBogdanovic":"o","HarrisonBarnes":"^","KevinDurant":"D","KhrisMiddleton":"s","LeBronJames":"o", "OttoPorterJr":"^","PaulGeorge":"D","TimHardawayJr":"s","TJWarren":"o"} 
    for name in playerlist:        
        plt.plot(FieldGoals[PlayerD[name]], c=Col[name], ls='--', marker=Mrk[name], ms=7, label=name)
    plt.legend(loc='upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1,1))
    plt.xticks(list(range(0,7)), Month)
    plt.show()

def FreeThrowsplot(playerlist=Players):
    Col = {"AndrewWiggins":"Black", "BojanBogdanovic":"Red","HarrisonBarnes":"Green","KevinDurant":"Blue","KhrisMiddleton":"Magenta","LeBronJames":"Black", "OttoPorterJr":"Red","PaulGeorge":"Green","TimHardawayJr":"Blue","TJWarren":"Magenta"}
    Mrk = {"AndrewWiggins":"s","BojanBogdanovic":"o","HarrisonBarnes":"^","KevinDurant":"D","KhrisMiddleton":"s","LeBronJames":"o", "OttoPorterJr":"^","PaulGeorge":"D","TimHardawayJr":"s","TJWarren":"o"} 
    for name in playerlist:        
        plt.plot(FreeThrowMade[PlayerD[name]], c=Col[name], ls='--', marker=Mrk[name], ms=7, label=name)

# Tallying up the points
Wiggins_tally = sum(Wiggins)
Barnes_tally = sum(Barnes)
Durant_tally = sum(Durant)
George_tally = sum(George)
Warren_tally = sum(Warren)

#x-Axis (Labels)
players_label = ['Andrew Wiggins','Harrison Barnes', 'Kevin Durant', 'Paul George', 'TJ Warren']
#Converting the X-Axis into an array
players_label_arr = np.array(players_label)

#Y-Axis (Values for the labels)
tally = [Wiggins_tally,Barnes_tally, Durant_tally, George_tally, Warren_tally]

#Plotting the Bar
plt.bar(players_label_arr,tally)

#Labelling X and Y axes
plt.xlabel('Player Names', fontsize = 20, color='DarkBlue')
plt.ylabel('Total Points', fontsize = 20, color='DarkBlue')

#The Title
plt.title("WC Small Forward - Final Rankings", fontsize=35, color="DarkBlue", fontname="Console")

#Displaying the Bar
plt.show()
